Products.SmallFormatDescription: Doritos Salsa Dip Mild
Products.FullDescription: Doritos Salsa Dip Mild
Products.RichDescription:
Doritos Mild Salsa is a Mexican Dip experience perfect for your Doritos to Dip and Crunch. This Salsa is free from spicy tastes, but packs a punch with tangy Mexican & tomato flavours to enhance your corn chips or crackers! Better yet, it contains no artificial colours or flavours, is suitable for vegetarians and is 99% fat free.

Load up your Doritos Corn Chips & Crackers with Mild Salsa Dip to unleash the full Doritos taste experience!

Mild Tangy salsa makes your snacking experience even bolder, is the perfect dip for sharing and is suitable for vegetarians containing no artificial colours or flavours.

If you’re looking for a more explosive taste experience, look up our Doritos Nachos recipe.

Doritos Salsa Dip, for the bold.
  • Mild Salsa
  • Goes great with corn chips and crackers
  • Perfect for sharing

Products.SmallFormatDescription: Masterfoods Sweet Plum Marinade
Products.FullDescription: Masterfoods Sweet Plum Marinade
Products.RichDescription:
MasterFoods Sweet Plum Marinade is made with delicate star anise and delicious sweet plums blended to capture the sweet & sour Asian flavour.

MasterFoods Sweet Plum Marinade is made with delicate star anise and delicious sweet plums blended to capture the sweet & sour Asian flavour.

To marinate simply...
- Cover meat generously with marinade and refrigerate for at least 20 minutes before cooking.
- For extra tenderness and flavour, marinate overnight in refrigerator.
- Simply BBQ, grill, pan fry or oven bake on medium heat.

Do not consume uncooked marinade that has been in contact with raw meat.

Try something different...with the Spring rolls with Sweet Plum Dipping Sauce:

Preparation Time: 5 mins, Cook: 20 mins, Serves: 6

What You'll Need:
Spring Rolls or Dim Sum 
1 MasterFoods Sweet Plum Marinade

How To Cook:
1. Cook spring rolls or your favourite Asian dim sum according to packet instructions.
2. Combine marinade with a dash of soy sauce.
3. Serve as a dipping sauce accompaniment.

Refrigerate after opening.

No Artificial Colours, Flavours or Preservatives.
